=== MIRROR_ROOM ===
# id: 9
# title: The Mirror Room
# chinese_title: 镜室
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

Every surface in this chamber has been polished to a mirror shine. Your reflection stares back at you from a hundred angles, but something is wrong — some reflections move a half-second too late. A small console sits at the center, its screen displaying symbols.

* [Interact with the console]
  ~ gain_radical("目")
  "目" (mù) — eye, to see
* [Examine your lagging reflections]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "镜" (jìng) — mirror
* [Smash a mirror to see what's behind it]
  ~ gain_item("nano_shield")
  "破" (pò) — to break, to shatter
